<title>USA: DSP Communications to buy back shares.</title>
<headline>DSP Communications to buy back shares.</headline>
<dateline>CUPERTINO, Calif. 1997-04-16</dateline>
<text>
<p>DSP Communications Inc said Wednesday its board authorized the repurchase of up to two million shares, or 44 percent of the total outstanding.</p>
<p>It said the repurchases would be made on the open-market and in privately negotiated transactions.</p>
